(2132, 1, '2015-11-12 14:24:55', '2015-11-12 14:24:55', '<b>Districts:</b> gewürztraminer is best known in wines from Alsace, Germany, the U.S. West Coast, and New York.\r\n\r\n<b>Typical taste</b> in varietal wine: fruity flavors with aromas of rose petals, peaches, lychees, and allspice. A Gewürztraminer seems generally not as refreshing as other types of dry whites.', 'Gewürztraminer', '<b>Food pairings:</b> gewürztraminer is ideal for sipping. It can fit Asian food, pork and grilled sausages.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'gewurztraminer', '', '', '2015-11-12 14:25:45', '2015-11-12 14:25:45', '', 0, 'http://tests.shahum.net/?post_type=product&#038;p=2132', 0, 'product', '', 0),
